# =============================================================================
# Nexus plugin dev repo — .gitignore
#
# This repo is the source of truth for the nexus / nexus-dotnet plugins. The
# entries below are LOCAL RUNTIME STATE generated while developing or testing
# the plugins in-place. Real artifacts that live in the same trees (pipeline
# specs under docs/specs/**, hook tests under plugins/**/__tests__/) are NOT
# ignored — they must be committed.
# =============================================================================

# --- Claude Code + Nexus pipeline local state -------------------------------
# Session/persona state written by the persona commands and pipeline hooks.
# Ignore the specific local files, not the whole .claude/ dir, so a shared
# .claude/settings.json (Claude Code convention) can still be tracked.
# NOTE: this does NOT match .claude-plugin/ (the tracked marketplace manifest).
.claude/.current-agent
.claude/.pipeline-state
.claude/.personas.json
.claude/settings.local.json

# --- Audit-trail output (ADR-11, opt-in) -------------------------------------
# Raw per-run capture read by the consumption-report skill. Regenerated each run.
# Current path is .claude/audit/ (1.3.0+); docs/audit/ kept for pre-1.3.0 strays.
.claude/audit/
docs/audit/

# --- Harness Cover runner output (Inc 2) -------------------------------------
# The Cover Workflow's runner agent Write()s its results here, NEXUS-SIDE, so they never strand in the
# sprint-rituals commit (cover.workflow.js: RUNS_DIR). Regenerated each run — local runtime state.
harness/.runs/

# --- Node (scripts/*.mjs may gain dependencies) -----------------------------
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Editor / IDE -----------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# --- OS noise ---------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
